{"tid":1538094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於903太子站傷者事實","createTime":"2019-09-04T06:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T06:26:14.000Z","uid":262185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d664e9d161437aa16ce003525311b77938b52a4b","tid":1538094,"uid":262185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:22:34.000Z","msg":"tg轉發<br />\n⚠️關於903太子站傷者事實⚠️<br />\n<br />\n1.醫管局回應，是次事件中共3名傷者，年齡為21歲至42歲<br />\n<br />\n2.於各大媒體訪問其父親及本頻度消息證實，事件中21歲傷者於救護車時已恢復意識，能說出家屬名稱及電話號碼<br />\n推出R房時，頸箍已除下，情況穩定<br />\n其父已確認這名21歲傷者為太子站曾昏迷男子<br />\n<br />\n3.關於網絡流傳15歲傷者，醫管局回覆未有是次事件傷者為15歲，據現場醫護及目擊者表示，未有見過15歲傷頸椎骨折的病患<br />\n<br />\n4.現場消息，曾有一位另一事件入院，坐輪椅的年輕傷者(非頸椎骨折症狀)於急症室出現，可能因此誤會<br />\n<br />\n如昨晚有廣華醫院醫護，曾處理過非21歲懷疑頸椎骨折病患或其家屬，請與我們聯絡<br />\n@fcairport_bot<br />\n<br />\nFrom tg channel 機場fact check資訊頻道<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/fcairport\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffcairport&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEq13VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=0cb4f446\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/fcairport</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/04/141841_7b5f8baa3d0d1ea69bc9b5600c8b3fa1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F04%2F141841_7b5f8baa3d0d1ea69bc9b5600c8b3fa1.jpeg&h=d8b5e7d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/04/141844_00b98d78e7541eb477ab78ab6310c40b.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F04%2F141844_00b98d78e7541eb477ab78ab6310c40b.jpeg&h=ba92fa3d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CzN3cnK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCzN3cnK.png&h=270c0643&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3cca7ae80ec71432cf52a5b072ea3a309d873825","tid":1538094,"uid":93563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:24:17.000Z","msg":"冇事都好la，希望係真相la"},{"pid":"fa677e